### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Criar Instância e Obter QR Code
POST http://localhost:3000/instances/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instanceId": "user_123"
}

### Verificar Status da Instância
GET http://localhost:3000/instances/user_123/status

### Enviar Mensagem
POST http://localhost:3000/messages/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instanceId": "user_123",
  "to": "5511999999999",
  "message": "Olá, sua fatura venceu"
}

### Listar Todas as Instâncias
GET http://localhost:3000/instances

### Remover Instância
DELETE http://localhost:3000/instances/user_123

